Name: Milf City
About the game: Milf City is a modern city where many races, cultures and lives of ordinary people are intertwined. And today you will be able to get to know more closely the life of 5 beautiful girls, residents of this city, who are radically different in their lifestyles and characters. Here you will forget about the problems of everyday life and plunge into the exciting world of Milf City! Features: ➡ 5 girls who will amaze you with their diversity and charisma! ➡ Once you start the game, you will not be able to stop, you will want more and more ... ➡ Mahjong-solitaire, in which you can show your flexibility of mind and receive the desired rewards ... ➡ Every girl has her own Mahjong-solitaire puzzle. ➡ Each girl has her own gallery, with her own unique pictures. About the characters: ➡ The owner of the beer bar is a sexy American woman who knows everything about brewing real beer and is not averse to having a couple of glasses with you while having a pleasant conversation. Very modest, she greedily absorbs compliments, like the earth on a hot day. ➡ Owner of a grocery supermarket. She loves to work with her hands and take care of plants.
